#Supplementary Method S2. Computational workflow
1.	ONT read quality assessment 
2.	ONT read filtering 
3.	Illumina read quality assessment 
4.	Hi-C library quality inspection 
5.	De novo genome assembly using Hifiasm 
6.	Extraction of the primary assembly 
7.	Genome quality assessment 
8.	Hi-C read alignment 
9.	Hi-C scaffolding evaluation 
10.	Structural validation using Hi-C contact maps 
11.	Manual inspection of Hi-C interaction maps 
12.	Structural and functional genome annotation 


