hic.sorted.bam

8.	Supplementary Method S4. Structural validation
Assembly structure was evaluated using Hi-C contact matrices generated from mapped Hi-C reads. Contact maps were visually inspected using Juicebox Assembly Tools (JBAT) to identify potential misassemblies, inversions, orientation errors, and spurious joins. 

